\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

th neighbor of 
\begin_inset Formula $\kappa$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial\kappa^{(f)}$
\end_inset

 be the 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

th face of 
\begin_inset Formula $\kappa$
\end_inset

, such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial\kappa=\bigcup_{f=1}^{n_{f}}\partial\kappa^{(f)}$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{f}$
\end_inset

 is the number of faces.
