reference "eq:CFL-condition-viscous-2D"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 are sufficient but not necessary for 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{y}_{\kappa,c}^{j+1}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{y}_{\kappa,v}^{j+1}$
